Suggested change so that you see what I mean:
```suggestion
        // Minimum codec size must be respected (regardless of requested maxSize)
        int minCodecSize = constraints.getMinCodecSize();
        int minSize = (minCodecSize + (alignment - 1)) / alignment * alignment;

        assert minSize <= maxCodecSize.width : "The minimum width cannot exceed the maximum codec width";
        assert minSize <= maxCodecSize.height : "The minimum height cannot exceed the maximum codec height";

        if (w < minSize) {
            w = minSize;
        }
